<section class="section section--alt who-i-work-with animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">For Owners Who Want Assets, Not Just Code</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          I don't work with everyone. I work best with business owners who have traction but are stuck in the "Founder's Trap."
        </p>
    </div>
      
    <div class="qualifier-grid">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="qualifier-card">
            <div class="qualifier-card__icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <strong>Revenue: $500k â€“ $5M</strong>
            <p>You have a proven business model, not just an idea. You have cash flow to invest in efficiency.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="qualifier-card">
            <div class="qualifier-card__icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <strong>Problem: Bottleneck</strong>
            <p>You are the only one who knows how the "secret sauce" works. If you take a vacation, the business stalls.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="qualifier-card">
            <div class="qualifier-card__icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="icon"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <strong>Goal: Systems</strong>
            <p>You want to move from "Operator" to "Owner." You need software assets that execute your process automatically.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Apple Style 3-Card Grid */
    .who-i-work-with {
        background-color: var(--color-surface);
        padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: var(--max-width-page);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--space-6);
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .section-intro {
        font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .qualifier-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .qualifier-card {
        background: var(--color-surface-alt);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 40px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .qualifier-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .qualifier-card__icon {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        background: var(--color-accent);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        color: white;
    }

    .qualifier-card__icon .icon {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
    }

    .qualifier-card strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .qualifier-card p {
        font-size: var(--font-size-base);
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .qualifier-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--space-md);
        }
    }
</style>
